channel.title: Looking for a 194 server developer
channel.description:
Hey guys, I am working on a website for my RSPS, but I need someone to work on the source/client as I am not that good with these. The website is going pretty good so far (I coded it from scratch). So, I am looking for someone to come aboard the team with me and make the source, and stuff. I can handle the website things, while this person does the source, fixing bugs, adding content, and so on. (Of course this person will be an admin or mod on the server)
If you are interested add me on skype, (Skype Name: Ian.Lind1)
If you are no interested please don't post about it.
You can check out the website so far, (WIP): [url=http://www.galaxyscape.netii.net]http://www.galaxyscape.netii.net[/url] (Please note that I will be buying a domain (GalaxyScape.net) very soon, I am just using a free host until we get things going)
Thanks :p
